<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Articles_connexes">Articles connexes</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Parti_philosophique&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=10" title="Modifier la section : Articles connexes" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor"><span>modifier</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Parti_philosophique&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Modifier le code source de la section : Articles connexes"><span>modifier le code</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Collaborateurs_de_l'Encyclopédie_(1751-1772)" class="mw-redirect" title="Collaborateurs de l&#39;Encyclopédie (1751-1772)">Collaborateurs de l'Encyclopédie (1751-1772)</a></li>
